frames.caption: A woman sits on a wooden bench by a river, cradling a fawn in her arms. Two deer stand close by, one nuzzling the fawn affectionately. The scene is set against a backdrop of lush green trees and a flowing river.
frames.description: The scene captures a serene moment in nature where a woman interacts with a group of deer by a river. The setting is peaceful, with autumn foliage and a gentle river adding to the tranquil atmosphere.

frames.caption: A woman sits on a wooden bench in a forested area, gently holding a fawn in her lap. Two other deer stand nearby, curiously observing the scene. The background features a flowing river and autumn-colored trees.
frames.description: The scene takes place in a serene forest setting during autumn, with a river flowing in the background. A woman is interacting with a group of deer, creating a peaceful and harmonious atmosphere.

frames.caption: A woman sits on a log in a forested area, gently holding a young deer in her lap. Two other deer stand nearby, one looking curiously at the camera while the other grazes. The scene is set against a backdrop of autumn foliage, creating a serene and natural atmosphere.
frames.description: The image depicts a tranquil moment in a forest during autumn. A woman interacts with several deer, highlighting a harmonious connection between humans and nature.
